ActFinancial Administration Act
Pilotage Act
SubjectGreat Lakes Pilotage Authority ** 2010-2014 CORPORATE PLAN **
PrecisOrder (a) approving the CORPORATE PLAN of the GREAT LAKES PILOTAGE AUTHORITY for the 2010 to 2014 calendar years; and (b) fixing the maximum amount of money the Authority may borrow, in Canada and elsewhere, to a maximum of CDN $6,000,000 for the purpose of defraying its expenses.
